commitResults.messageTitle: Add assertions to Task constructor method.
commitResults.messageBody:
To help to document the assumption that tasks must have non-empty, non-null descriptions

To ensure that the input parameters for description is not-empty and non-null

The assertion makes sure that if it is violated during runtime, an assertion error will be thrown, providing valuable information for debugging
